  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.5.3">
<l>uṭampuruvil mūṉṟoṉṟāy mūrtti vēṟā yulakuyya niṉṟāṉai yaṉṟu pēycci</l>
<l>viṭamparuku vittakaṉaik kaṉṟu mēyttu viḷaiyāṭa vallāṉai varaimī kāṉil,</l>
<l>taṭamparuku karumukilait tañcaik kōyil tavaneṟikkōr peruneṟiyai vaiyaṅ kākkum</l>
<l>kaṭumparimēl kaṟkiyaināṉ kaṇṭu koṇṭēṉ kaṭipoḻilcūḻ kaṭaṉmallait talaca yaṉattē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who endures becoming varied forms to save the world,</l>
<l rend="indent">as the one among three embodied forms,</l>
<l>The clever one who once drank the demoness’ poison,</l>
<l rend="indent">the god who played [at] grazing the calves,</l>
<l>A dark cloud which sips [from] pools in jungles on the mountain peaks,</l>
<l rend="indent">the path in the Tañcai temple greater than the path of penance,</l>
<l>Kalki on a speeding horse who protects the world, I saw for myself</l>
<l rend="indent">in Talacayaṉam encircled by fragrant gardens at Mallai by the sea.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
